Follow the Kalevea UI system.

Reference docs:

* docs/design/kalevea-ui-system.md
* docs/architecture/frontend-ui-architecture.md
* AGENTS.md

Rules:

* Prefer shared components from components/system.
* Avoid module-specific UI duplication.
* Use Tailwind consistently.
* Maintain accessibility and keyboard navigation.
* Avoid generic dashboard styling.
* Prefer workspace layouts and entity panels.
